'''Mendel, Gregor (1822-1884)'''

B' e [[manach]] às an [[an Ostair|Ostair]] a bha ann am '''Mendel'''. B' e esan a’ chiad duine a thoirt cunntas saidheansail air na [[gine]]an, no air “na factaran”, mar a thug e fhèin orra. Thaisbean Mendel gur e tro na ginean sin gum bheirear cuid de stilean an athair neo na mathair air an clann.  

